        "bodyContent": "=<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head><style>body{font-family:Arial,sans-serif;line-height:1.6;color:#333;}.header{background:#2c5aa0;color:white;padding:20px;text-align:center;}.content{padding:20px;}.button{display:inline-block;padding:12px 24px;background:#28a745;color:white;text-decoration:none;border-radius:5px;margin:20px 0;}</style></head>\n<body>\n<div class=\"header\"><h1>🎉 Your Template is Ready!</h1></div>\n<div class=\"content\">\n<p>Hi {{ $('Parse Webhook Data').item.json.webhookData.customerName || 'Customer' }},</p>\n<p>Thank you for purchasing the <strong>{{ $('Find Marketplace Product in Boost.space').first().json.name || $('Parse Webhook Data').item.json.templateName }}</strong> template!</p>\n<h2>📥 Download Your Template</h2>\n<p><a href=\"{{ $('Generate Download Link').json.downloadLink }}\" class=\"button\">Download Now (Expires in 7 days)</a></p>\n<h2>⚡ Need n8n Cloud?</h2>\n<p>We recommend n8n Cloud for the best experience. <a href=\"https://tinyurl.com/ym3awuke\">Get started here</a></p>\n<p><small>Benefits: Automatic updates, cloud hosting, 24/7 support</small></p>\n<h2>📚 Setup Instructions</h2>\n<p>1. Import the workflow JSON file into your n8n instance</p>\n<p>2. Configure credentials (Airtable, Slack, etc.)</p>\n<p>3. Test the workflow</p>\n<p>Need help? Reply to this email or book a setup call.</p>\n<p>Best regards,<br>The Rensto Team<br>service@rensto.com</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>",
